Description_lang: Healing Tide Totem's cooldown is reduced by ${$s1/-1000} sec and it heals for $s2% more each time it pulses.

description_blz.en_US: Healing Tide Totem's cooldown is reduced by 45 sec and it heals for 25% more each time it pulses.
